---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us | Author's Choice" description="Find answers to the most common questions about Author's Choice technical writing program.">
  <Header />

 <section id="about" class="about section-lg">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-header fade-in">
      <h2 class="section-title">
        About <span class="text-gradient">Author's Choice</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="about-subtitle">
        Transforming lives through the power of technical writing ‚Äî because everyone deserves a path to financial freedom.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mission-vision-grid fade-in stagger-1">
      <div class="mission-card card scale-in stagger-1">
        <div class="card-icon">üéØ</div>
        <h3>Our Mission</h3>
        <p>To democratize access to high-paying tech careers by teaching ambitious people from all backgrounds how to become six-figure technical writers ‚Äî no degree, no license, no prior tech experience required.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="vision-card card scale-in stagger-2">
        <div class="card-icon">üåü</div>
        <h3>Our Vision</h3>
        <p>A world where your background doesn't determine your future ‚Äî where factory workers, immigrants, freelancers, and career changers can all build respected, well-paid careers in tech through the power of clear communication.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="founder-story fade-in stagger-2">
      <div class="story-header">
        <h3>The Story Behind Author's Choice</h3>
        <p class="story-subtitle">From Factory Floor to Six-Figure Success</p>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-story">
        <div class="story-item fade-in stagger-1">
          <div class="story-year">2020</div>
          <div class="story-content">
            <div class="story-image">
              <img 
                src="/s4.jpg" 
                alt="Factory worker in manufacturing environment"
                class="story-img"
              />
              <div class="story-overlay">
                <span class="story-status">The Beginning</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="story-text">
              <h4>Factory Worker</h4>
              <p>Like many of you, I started working in a factory. Long hours, physical demands, and limited growth opportunities. I knew there had to be something better, but I didn't know what or how to get there.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="story-item fade-in stagger-2">
          <div class="story-year">2021</div>
          <div class="story-content">
            <div class="story-image">
              <img 
                src="/s2.jpg" 
                alt="Exhausted worker looking for opportunities"
                class="story-img"
              />
              <div class="story-overlay">
                <span class="story-status">The Struggle</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="story-text">
              <h4>Exhausted & Searching</h4>
              <p>By 2021, I was completely burnt out. Working long shifts, coming home exhausted, with barely enough energy to think about my future. I started desperately searching for better opportunities ‚Äî something that would use my brain, not just my body.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="story-item fade-in stagger-3">
          <div class="story-year">2022</div>
          <div class="story-content">
            <div class="story-image">
              <img 
                src="/s3.jpg" 
                alt="Person learning technical writing on computer"
                class="story-img"
              />
              <div class="story-overlay">
                <span class="story-status">The Discovery</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="story-text">
              <h4>Found Technical Writing</h4>
              <p>That's when I discovered technical writing. I realized that my ability to explain complex processes clearly ‚Äî something I'd done informally at the factory ‚Äî was actually a valuable, high-paying skill in the tech world. I dove in headfirst, learning everything I could.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="story-item fade-in stagger-4">
          <div class="story-year">2023</div>
          <div class="story-content">
            <div class="story-image">
              <img 
                src="/s6.jpg" 
                alt="Professional technical writer at work"
                class="story-img"
              />
              <div class="story-overlay">
                <span class="story-status">The Breakthrough</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="story-text">
              <h4>Landed My First Tech Job</h4>
              <p>After months of dedicated learning and building my portfolio, I landed my first technical writing position at a tech company. The salary was more than double what I made at the factory, and for the first time, I felt respected and valued for my skills.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="story-item fade-in stagger-5">
          <div class="story-year">2024-2025</div>
          <div class="story-content">
            <div class="story-image">
              <img 
                src="/s5.jpg" 
                alt="Successful entrepreneur teaching others"
                class="story-img"
              />
              <div class="story-overlay">
                <span class="story-status pulse">Six Figures</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="story-text">
              <h4>Six-Figure Success & Giving Back</h4>
              <p>Today, I'm earning six figures as a technical writer and have built Author's Choice to help others make the same transformation. If a factory worker with no tech background can do it, so can you. Your background doesn't define your future ‚Äî your determination does.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="transformation-stats fade-in">
      <h3>My Transformation in Numbers</h3>
      <div class="stats-grid">
        <div class="transformation-stat scale-in stagger-1">
          <div class="stat-icon">üìà</div>
          <div class="stat-number">300%+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Salary Increase</div>
        </div>
        <div class="transformation-stat scale-in stagger-2">
          <div class="stat-icon">‚è∞</div>
          <div class="stat-number">18</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Months to Six Figures</div>
        </div>
        <div class="transformation-stat scale-in stagger-3">
          <div class="stat-icon">üè†</div>
          <div class="stat-number">100%</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Remote Work</div>
        </div>
        <div class="transformation-stat scale-in stagger-4">
          <div class="stat-icon">üéì</div>
          <div class="stat-number">0</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Degrees Required</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="why-we-exist fade-in">
      <div class="exist-content">
        <h3>Why Author's Choice Exists</h3>
        <p class="exist-text">
          I created Author's Choice because I know what it's like to feel stuck, undervalued, and unsure about your future. I know the frustration of working hard but not getting ahead. And I know the incredible feeling of finally finding a career that respects your intelligence and pays you what you're worth.
        </p>
        <p class="exist-text">
          <strong>This program isn't just about teaching technical writing ‚Äî it's about proving that your background doesn't limit your potential.</strong> Whether you're a factory worker, immigrant, freelancer, or career changer, you have the ability to build a six-figure career in tech. You just need the right roadmap.
        </p>
        <div class="founder-signature">
          <div class="signature-line"></div>
          <p class="signature-text">Founder & Lead Instructor, Shola Olujobi</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="values-section fade-in">
      <h3>Our Core Values</h3>
      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-card card scale-in stagger-1">
          <div class="value-icon">ü§ù</div>
          <h4>Inclusivity</h4>
          <p>We believe talent exists everywhere, regardless of background, education, or experience. Everyone deserves a chance to succeed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card card scale-in stagger-2">
          <div class="value-icon">üéØ</div>
          <h4>Results-Focused</h4>
          <p>We're not here to waste your time. Every lesson, assignment, and strategy is designed to get you hired and earning more.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card card scale-in stagger-3">
          <div class="value-icon">üí™</div>
          <h4>Empowerment</h4>
          <p>We don't just teach skills ‚Äî we build confidence, professional identity, and the mindset needed for long-term success.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card card scale-in stagger-4">
          <div class="value-icon">üå±</div>
          <h4>Growth</h4>
          <p>Your success doesn't end at graduation. We're committed to your continued growth and career advancement.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

   <div class="program-cta fade-in">
      <h3>Ready to Transform Your Writing Career?</h3>
      <p>Join our next cohort and start earning what you're worth as a technical writer.</p>
      <a href="#enroll" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Join Now</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
<style>

.program-cta {
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    color: white;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .program-cta::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%;
    left: -50%;
    width: 200%;
    height: 200%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
    animation: rotate 20s linear infinite;
  }

  @keyframes rotate {
    0% {
      transform: rotate(0deg);
    }
    100% {
      transform: rotate(360deg);
    }
  }

  .program-cta h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .program-cta p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .program-cta .btn {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .program-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
    }

    .program-modules {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .program-cta h3 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .program-cta p {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
    }

    .module-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.01);
    }
  }

  .about {
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.05) 0%, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.05) 0%, transparent 50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .about-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .about-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .mission-vision-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(400px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  .mission-card,
  .vision-card {
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .mission-card::before {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(30, 58, 138, 0.1) 0%, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1) 100%);
  }

  .vision-card::before {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.1) 0%, rgba(234, 88, 12, 0.1) 100%);
  }

  .mission-card::before,
  .vision-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .mission-card:hover::before,
  .vision-card:hover::before {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .card-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    display: block;
  }

  .mission-card h3,
  .vision-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .mission-card p,
  .vision-card p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .founder-story {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .story-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .story-header h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .story-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: #f97316;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .timeline-story {
    position: relative;
  }

  .timeline-story::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    /* background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #3b82f6 50%, #f97316 100%); */
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .story-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .story-item:nth-child(even) {
    flex-direction: row-reverse;
  }

  .story-item:nth-child(even) .story-content {
    flex-direction: row-reverse;
  }

  .story-item:nth-child(even) .story-text {
    text-align: right;
  }

  .story-year {
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    top: -10%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
    color: white;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(30, 58, 138, 0.3);
    z-index: 2;
    min-width: 100px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .story-content {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0 3rem;
  }

  .story-image {
    position: relative;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px var(--card-shadow-hover);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .story-image:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .story-img {
    width: 250px;
    height: 300px;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .story-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(transparent, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8));
    padding: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .story-status {
    color: white;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .story-text {
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 400px;
  }

  .story-text h4 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .story-text p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .transformation-stats {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .transformation-stats::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%;
    left: -50%;
    width: 200%;
    height: 200%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
    animation: rotate 25s linear infinite;
  }

  .transformation-stats h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .transformation-stat {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .transformation-stat:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .stat-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: block;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: #fbbf24;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .why-we-exist {
    background: var(--bg-tertiary);
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .exist-content h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .exist-text {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .founder-signature {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .signature-line {
    width: 200px;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1e3a8a, #f97316);
    margin: 0 auto 1rem;
  }

  .signature-text {
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  .values-section {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .values-section h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .value-card {
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  }

  .value-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px) scale(1.02);
  }

  .value-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: block;
  }

  .value-card h4 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .value-card p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  .about-cta {
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316 0%, #ea580c 100%);
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    color: white;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about-cta::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%;
    left: -50%;
    width: 200%;
    height: 200%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
    animation: rotate 20s linear infinite;
  }

  .about-cta h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .about-cta p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .about-cta .btn {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .mission-vision-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .timeline-story::before {
      left: 2rem;
    }

    .story-item {
      flex-direction: column !important;
      text-align: center;
      padding-left: 4rem;
    }

    .story-item:nth-child(even) .story-content {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .story-item:nth-child(even) .story-text {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .story-year {
      left: 2rem;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
    }

    .story-content {
      flex-direction: column;
      padding: 0;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .story-img {
      width: 150px;
      height: 120px;
    }

    .stats-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .values-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .about-cta h3 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .about-cta p {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
    }
  }
</style>